high_descs: Turn around to reach the coffeetable.
Pick up the spoon next to the plate from the table.
Turn around and walk to the bathroom on the right and reach the sink.
Put the spoon in the sink to wash it and take it out.
Move left to face the sink.
Put the spoon on top of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed spoon on top of the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the coffeetable behind you.
Pick up the spoon off of the table.
Turn around and go into the bathroom on the right.
Put the spoon in the sink, turn of water on and rinse it off and then take it out.
Put the spoon on the upper left ledge of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a Spoon off and put it on the Sink ledge.

high_descs: Turn right and again turn move towards the coffeetable.
Pick  the spoon from the coffeetable.
Turn left and again turn left and turn left move towards the sink.
Place the spoon on the sink, pick the spoon from the sink.
Turn left and move towards the sink.
Place the spoon inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: To place the spoon inside the sink.
